### Priority 1 — CRITICAL (Must fix before scaling)

| # | Issue | Risk | File | Fix |
|---|-------|------|------|-----|
| 1 | **Pool max: 20** — exhausts at ~200 users | 💀 HIGH | [config/index.js](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/config/index.js#L87) | Increase to 50, or use PgBouncer |
| 2 | **OpenAPI pool.on('error') calls process.exit(-1)** | 💀 HIGH | [openapi/db/postgres.js](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/openapi/src/db/postgres.js#L33) | Remove `process.exit(-1)` |
| 3 | **`/api/stats` — no cache, 5 COUNT scans** | 🔴 HIGH | [routes/index.js](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/routes/index.js#L39) | Redis cache with 60s TTL |
| 4 | **`getComments()` — wasted query** | 🔴 HIGH | [scripts.service.js](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/modules/scripts/scripts.service.js#L394) | Remove first unused query |

### Priority 2 — HIGH (Fix within 1 week of launch)

| # | Issue | Risk | File | Fix |
|---|-------|------|------|-----|
| 5 | **`getScriptBySlug` — `id::text` cast** | 🟠 HIGH | [scripts.service.js:124](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/modules/scripts/scripts.service.js#L124) | Use separate `OR s.id = $1::uuid` with try-catch |
| 6 | **Browse scripts — no response cache** | 🟠 HIGH | scripts.service.js | Add Redis cache 30s TTL |
| 7 | **`toggleLike()` — no transaction, race condition** | 🟠 HIGH | [scripts.service.js:373](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/modules/scripts/scripts.service.js#L373) | Wrap in transaction or use CTE |
| 8 | **`getScriptsByOwner()` — no pagination** | 🟠 HIGH | [scripts.service.js:57](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/modules/scripts/scripts.service.js#L57) | Add LIMIT/OFFSET |
| 9 | **`getScriptsByHub()` — no pagination** | 🟠 MED | [scripts.service.js:72](file:///c:/docker/next-js/scripthub.id/backend/src/modules/scripts/scripts.service.js#L72) | Add LIMIT/OFFSET |

### Priority 3 — MEDIUM (Fix within 1 month)

| # | Issue | Risk | File | Fix |
|---|-------|------|------|-----|
| 10 | **Sequential COUNT + SELECT** in browse & deployments | 🟡 MED | scripts.service.js, deployments.service.js | Use `Promise.all()` or window fn |
| 11 | **SELECT \* everywhere** | 🟡 MED | Multiple files | Select only needed columns |
| 12 | **No compression middleware** | 🟡 MED | app.js | Add `compression()` middleware |
