| 14 | **Tags/Games — no response cache** | 🟡 LOW | tags.service.js, games.service.js | Redis cache 300s TTL |

### Priority 4 — LOW (Nice to have)

| # | Issue | Risk | File | Fix |
|---|-------|------|------|-----|
| 15 | **`ILIKE '%query%'` — always seq scan** | 🟢 LOW | scripts.service.js | Add `pg_trgm` extension + GIN index for text search |
| 16 | **Pool config hardcoded** | 🟢 LOW | config/index.js | Make `max` an env var: `DB_POOL_MAX` |
| 17 | **Monetization cleanup — no scheduler** | 🟢 LOW | monetization.service.js | Add `node-cron` to run `cleanupExpiredSessions()` hourly |

